Package: tlframe
Title: Clinical Tables, Figures, and Listings for Regulatory Submission
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Vignesh", "Thanikachalam", email = "about.vignesh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Produces regulatory-grade clinical trial tables, listings, and
    figures (TLFs) in RTF and PDF from a single specification. Designed for
    pharmaceutical industry workflows with support for paginated output,
    spanning headers, decimal alignment, programmatic page headers/footers,
    and company-specific rule presets. Built on disciplined S3 classes with
    a clean, composable pipeline API. No 'dplyr', 'tidyr', or 'purrr'
    dependency — only lightweight infrastructure packages ('rlang', 'cli',
    'vctrs').
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/vthanik/tlframe
BugReports: https://github.com/vthanik/tlframe/issues
